<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n01118i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n01" href="#n01118i">N01 (VI.B.10)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n01all.htm#n01118i"> 118(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> disgraceful abominable / old woman = wife (Jap)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[GLIMPSES AT JAPAN]</font> It is extremely difficult for the foreigner to penetrate into the real home-life of a Japanese <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> Our host advances and greets us with a low obeisance <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> We are now introduced to his &ldquo;<mark>disgraceful and abominable old woman&rdquo; (wife)</mark> <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> The ladies are also wearing the <i>obi</i>, a belt a foot wide, which is wound round the body over the <i>kimono</i>. <small> <a name="IT27jan23" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#IT27jan23"><cite title="source">Irish Times</cite></a> (27 January 1923) 10/2</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c05167m" href="c05all.htm#c05167m">VI.C.05:167(m)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
